node.text: Here’s a breakdown to get the beachy waves I’ve been rocking recently! I’m obsessed with this look and it lasts for daysss. It is my FAVORITE look, please try and let me know how it goes!! Pop in some dry-shampoo in between the layers and don’t forget to wash with @redken hair cleansing cream 1-2 times a month in addition to your usual (semi)daily shampoo routine 🥰🙏🏼 #ad

node.title: Shakira waves tutorial! Ft @redken and a whole lotta hair ❤️

node.text:
*not that I’m an expert at anything but I feel I have this look down alright☺️*
1️⃣quench @tarte moisturizing primer
2️⃣armani luminous silk 5.5 mix with Tarte h2o
3️⃣SHAPE TAPE by tarte cuz I gotta hide these dark circles
4️⃣peach perfect powder
5️⃣sugar rush bronzer
6️⃣tarteist pro glow
7️⃣mac clear brown set + Tarte powder
8️⃣too faced natural lust silk robe
9️⃣tarte maneater mascara
🔟 setting spray - smashbox + Tarte stay spray
.
Lash extensions - @fvckmascara
Hairrr - @hairby_chrissy
.
I use a lot of Tarte goodies, as you can see, and they’ve gifted me with a coupon code for you for the holidays!! “Nikki” will save you 15% at Tarte.com - 🎄✨🎅🏽 Ho Ho Ho merry Christmas amirite LOVE YOU GUYZ

node.text:
Thought I would drop my recent routine for warmup & glute activation for leg day!!
🌶😮‍💨🍒 like & save for later and don’t forget your warmups and cool downs 🥰💖

☆ warmup and stretch:
- 50 jumping jacks (get the heart rate goinnn)
- 20 slow, deep walking lunges
- 15 Saigon squat to hamstring stretch
- 15 side to side groin hamstring stretch

☆glute activation
- 15 banded glute bridges
- 10 banded side leg raises (per leg)
- 10 banded kick backs (per leg)
- 10 banded lateral lunges (per leg)

Wearing: @gymshark apex top, training shorts
Bands from @suzie_kb

node.text:
Full Body Sweat 💖🍒🧚🏼‍♀️
Be ready to feel the burnnn, this workout was so bomb!! Like and save for laterrr for a challenge ✨ *hopefully I uploaded this correctly this time lol*

Warm Up
🌼band walk (incline) x20 
🍓walking lunges x20

Circuit 1:
🌴 reverse lunge into a press x10 per leg
💐 jumping banded squats x15
☀️ med ball slams x10-12
Repeat 3x

Circuit 2:
🌴 overhead side lunge into front lunge x10 per leg
🧚🏼‍♀️ explosive glute bridge x10 per leg
🥞 decline push ups x10 
Repeat 3x

Circuit 3: 
🍒  t bar squat x12
🐉 mat jumps x12
🦋 alternating hand to toe (abs) x15 per side
Repeat 3x

Wearing @gymshark 🦈 flex shorts - size small; training bandeau bra - size small
Pre-workout: @alaninutrition breezeberry 🫐 
Bands: @suzie_kb

node.text:
Day after this workout 🏋️‍♂️ my “underbutt” is sore af, highly recommend 💖

Workout is at the end if you want to screenshot it! But I’ll put it here too:

Warm Up
🍀5 min incline treadmill
🌼Lateral band walk (incline) 20 per side x3
🍓Frog pump 15 x3

Circuit 1:
💐Side lunge + sumo RDL ( 10 reps right leg, 10 left leg, 10 RDL)
☀️heels up squat 12 reps
Repeat 4x

Circuit 2:
🌴Bulgarian split squats 10 reps per leg
🧚🏼‍♀️Knees to chest (abs) 15 reps
Repeat 3x

Circuit 3: 
🍒Side step up 10 reps per leg
🐉Renegade row 10 reps per arm
🦋Jump lunge 20 reps
Repeat 3x

Wearing @gymshark 
Bands: @suzie_kb
